Body: Thanks for reaching out. It’s my passion to help others find the career that they truly deserve especially in unprecedented times like these.    Sometimes we all need an extra boost, and that’s where I come in.    Send over a copy of your current resume for a courtesy review to Robert@CareerServiceStation.com and/or setup a courtesy call at http://meetme.so/RobertBraathe    Robert

Two questions I am often asked:  Does a writer need to be in my industry to be effective?  What will make my resume stand out? It starts with having a professional resume writer who can capture YOUR experiences, turning them into milestones, allowing YOUR skills and expertise to be the focus, while telling YOUR story in an elevated manner. I specialize in all levels and industries, designing the resume and wordsmithing the content to showcase YOUR capabilities. Also, I work within the guidelines of Applicant Tracking Software. If you are unaware, ATS is what is causing so many qualified people to be discounted before even getting an interview. HR often uses ATS to pre-screen and return a compatibility score on candidates. It’s an extremely sensitive algorithm that tells a human if you’re the right candidate. The program ISN’T able to read between the lines to understand your skills and expertise. Someone who can work within that process is vital to your success. That way you are not defeated before you start. SPECIAL $25 Off / Purchase by  March 28 th!! Good morning!  I have been writing and revising resumes most of my career!  It’s always challenging to write your own resume since we tend to lose perspective on what we do and have done that sets us apart. It’s always helpful to have an objective “set of eyes” help you present your best professional self.   I will work with you to understand your unique skills, talents, and accomplishments, and present them in a contemporary format.  We will then review the draft to ensure that the final product represents you in the strongest possible way!  Many job seekers undersell themselves and I will work with you to identify and spotlight your strongest skill sets and what makes you “uniquely” you and move the narrative to the next role you seek.   I invite you to view my services page and see what others have experienced!  https://www.linkedin.com/services/page/a806743078b0914a34  My service charge will be $425.  Happy to answer questions and look forward to working together!  Best,  Sharon Goldstein, M.S., CPC SFG Consulting, LLC sfgconsultingllc.com
